# StartupLens AI

An AI-powered platform that analyzes startup ideas and generates insights to help entrepreneurs validate and improve their business concepts.

## ✨ Features

- AI-powered startup idea analysis
- Business validation
- MVP recommendations
- Monetization suggestions
- Launch roadmap generation

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- Next.js 15
- TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS
- PostgreSQL
- Prisma ORM
- Auth.js
- Gemini API
